txt.en: Defeat elk in the Bruinen Gorges
There are elk dwelling in the Bruinen Gorges in the Trollshaws.\n\nThe wolves which trouble the Bruinen Gorges might be deterred if the number of the elk were thinned, leaving them with little prey.
